<span id="freeTextContainer13805723396129416994">I had read All My Love, Detrick by Roberta Kagan, the first book in this series, several months ago and although I still have several books that I have won in giveaways to read and review, I picked up You are My Sunshine: A Holocaust Novel and once I started reading it I could not put it down. I highly recommend this book. It was one of the best books I have read this summer. </span>

