<span id="freeTextContainer536936412517243076">I’m an American writer of Jewish and Romany decent. I write Historical Fiction and Historical Romance, most of which is set during the holocaust. Although I never discount the horrors of the time period, the main focus of my work is on ordinary people who prove to be strong heroic characters in unfathomable circumstances.<br/><br/>Facebook Author page:<br/><a target='_blank' rel='noopener nofollow' href='http://www.facebook.com/Rkagan4'>http://www.facebook.com/Rkagan4</a><br/><br/>Facebook Book Club:<br/><a target='_blank' rel='noopener nofollow' href='https://www.facebook.com/groups/1494285400798292/'>https:</a></span>
